    <item>
      <title>韩联社称韩国官员认为有必要增加美国能源进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/korea-official-sees-need-to-lift-us-energy-imports-yonhap-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩联社周日援引贸易部长的话称，韩国有能力购买更多美国能源，其成本与中东进口能源相比具有竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/korea-official-sees-need-to-lift-us-energy-imports-yonhap-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 02:48:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风暴和罢工过后美国就业增长有望迅速回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/us-job-growth-due-for-snapback-after-storms-and-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在飓风和大规模罢工削弱了上个月的就业增长之后，美国 11 月份的招聘人数可能出现增长，这与劳动力市场健康但逐渐降温的状况相一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/us-job-growth-due-for-snapback-after-storms-and-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《信用周刊》：债券义勇军颠覆法国债务市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/bond-vigilantes-upend-france-s-debt-market-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于信贷交易员担心财政计划可能会导致推翻政府，法国一些最大的公司的借贷成本现在低于主权国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/bond-vigilantes-upend-france-s-debt-market-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑色星期五销售加速，线上销售成为亮点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/black-friday-sales-accelerate-with-online-spending-a-bright-spot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，美国的“黑色星期五”销售额增长速度更快，凸显出挑剔的消费者在找到合适的产品时仍会打开钱包。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/black-friday-sales-accelerate-with-online-spending-a-bright-spot</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 18:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称特鲁多承诺在关税威胁后采取行动解决边境问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/trump-says-trudeau-pledged-action-on-border-after-tariff-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统唐纳德·特朗普与加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多在海湖庄园共进晚餐，旨在避免关税战。在此之后，加拿大正研究向美国边境增加更多资源和人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/trump-says-trudeau-pledged-action-on-border-after-tariff-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 18:34:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求金砖国家对使用美元作出“承诺”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/trump-demands-commitment-from-brics-nations-on-using-us-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普警告所谓的金砖国家，他将要求它们承诺不会创建新货币来替代美元，并多次威胁征收 100% 的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/trump-demands-commitment-from-brics-nations-on-using-us-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 18:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gautam Adani 称该组织每次袭击后都会变得更加强大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/adani-says-no-company-officials-are-facing-us-bribery-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 自美国检察官以 2.5 亿美元贿赂案起诉他以来首次公开发表讲话，语气激烈，他表示“每一次攻击”都会使他的企业集团更加强大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/adani-says-no-company-officials-are-facing-us-bribery-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 17:23:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚总统承诺在暴力冲突后继续留任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/georgian-police-begin-clearing-streets-after-protesters-regroup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚总统萨洛梅·祖拉比奇维利誓言将继续执政，拒绝接受执政党更换她的计划，并表示十月的议会选举不合法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-30/georgian-police-begin-clearing-streets-after-protesters-regroup</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Nov 2024 03:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
